## Tooling Capabilities

The agent can dynamically decide to call tools, including:

- 🔍 Web Search
- 🕷️ Web Scraping
- 📥 Resource Download
- 💻 Terminal Command Execution
- 📄 PDF Generation
- 🧾 File Read / Write
- 🍽️ Nutrition & Recipe Search (via MCP + Spoonacular)

MCP tools are automatically discovered and wrapped as LangChain tools at runtime.

